org.openimaj.feature.local

Interface LocalFeatureExtractor<FEATURE extends LocalFeature<?,?>,OBJECT>

  • Type Parameters:
    FEATURE - Type of local feature
    OBJECT - Type of object
    All Superinterfaces:
    FeatureExtractor<List<? extends FEATURE>,OBJECT>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    LocalFeatureMode.AbstractDoGSIFTModeOp, LocalFeatureMode.LocalFeatureModeOp

    public interface LocalFeatureExtractor<FEATURE extends LocalFeature<?,?>,OBJECT>
extends FeatureExtractor<List<? extends FEATURE>,OBJECT>
    Interface for objects capable of extracting local features from a given object. It is expected that implementors of this interface are threadsafe and can allow multiple calls to FeatureExtractor.extractFeature(Object) at the same time (or they at least synchronise the method).
    Author:
    Jonathon Hare (jsh2@ecs.soton.ac.uk)
